    javafx.fxml.Initializable, view.View

    public class MainWindowController
extends java.util.Observable
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable, view.View
    The mainWindowController class is the controller of our prime window this class managing all our communication with user that includes the presentation to the user and getting what the user want to the and convey it to the Controller with the help of the Observer pattern
